>\n好家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:08:34.000Z","msg":"老豆無咁多時間分配俾咁多仔女就梗㗎啦<br />\n聽落個老母都好冷血，好似當幾個仔女係籌碼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:15:18.000Z","msg":"睇過超盈一個訪問，佢話佢人生入面對佢最好同最親果個係自細湊大佢既一個老工人，因為老豆就太多仔女所以冇時間理佢而老母就重男輕女，都係冇咩點理佢"},{"pid":"43c5c1846d96b2d7569f445d36041c6c96822475","tid":1053402,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"日日上報"},{"pid":"59af714cea984a102e85a82193e7b6e4ff42a558","tid":1053402,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24919a3bfa887aab23f1f1a23e493dda464e1515","tid":1053402,"uid":136952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:11:49.000Z","msg":"原來個男朋友得廿歲<br />\n仲讀緊哈佛<br />\n唔怪之得唔show樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:21:15.000Z","msg":"超盈28喎，大八年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc66feac77dffe611aa8b80432cc90c969ae4755","tid":1053402,"uid":150320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:25:14.000Z","msg":"其實佢屌唔屌得何超蓮"},{"pid":"b5c3aae0b903193e7fffb188af8f8057a4faac98","tid":1053402,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4dd4e3bc12fe8b2524a9d9de53567c43f7dd671","tid":1053402,"uid":221790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"有冇一齊索K"},{"pid":"fe4d687e6982207b31f9004529029023d1d73d60","tid":1053402,"uid":171594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b5c3aae0b903193e7fffb188af8f8057a4faac98","tid":1053402,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:59:03.000Z","msg":"我真係冇父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7de4f56e22645fad71aa0851dc6c1a672948d4","tid":105